import styled from "styled-components"

const PList = styled.div``;
const PListItem = styled.div``;
const Image = styled.img``;
const PListItemTitles = styled.div``;
const PListItemTextB = styled.h1``;
const PListItemTextS = styled.h2``;

const PropertyList = () => {
  return (
    <PList>
      <PListItem>
        <Image src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/4023389/pexels-photo-4023389.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1" alt=""/>
        <PListItemTitles>Hotels</PListItemTitles>
        <PListItemTextS>2333 Hotels </PListItemTextS>
      </PListItem>
      <PListItem>
        <Image src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/338523/pexels-photo-338523.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1" alt=""/>
        <PListItemTitles>Resorts</PListItemTitles>
        <PListItemTextS>2338 Resorts </PListItemTextS>
      </PListItem>
      <PListItem>
        <Image src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1438834/pexels-photo-1438834.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1" alt=""/>
        <PListItemTitles>Villas</PListItemTitles>
        <PListItemTextS>2330 Villas </PListItemTextS>
      </PListItem>
      <PListItem>
        <Image src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/206648/pexels-photo-206648.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1" alt=""/>
        <PListItemTitles>Cabins</PListItemTitles>
        <PListItemTextS>2331 Cabins </PListItemTextS>
      </PListItem>
      <PListItem>
        <Image src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/2994300/pexels-photo-2994300.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=400" alt=""/>
        <PListItemTitles>Motels</PListItemTitles>
        <PListItemTextS>2337 Motels </PListItemTextS>
      </PListItem>
      <PListItem>
        <Image src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1571460/pexels-photo-1571460.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=400" alt=""/>
        <PListItemTitles>Apartments</PListItemTitles>
        <PListItemTextS>2337 Apartments </PListItemTextS>
      </PListItem>
    </PList>
  )
}

export default PropertyList
